[p 
	"	extra slashes here are to power up the berserker rage, which does 1.5 to double damage. and its not powered up as fast as possible... theres a slight delay so the last swipe catches the first boss.
	$LF
	"	the enemy manipulation here is a pain is the @$$! movement, current position, direction facing and buttons pressed seem to attribute to their behavior all at the same time. so getting them all to "come on down" took a little time. strangely enough, i lucked out the first time and killed them all very quickly.
	$LF
	"	oh, and slight delay is to ensure both enemies get the full force of the combo, but sometimes it isnt necessary.
